# Axodus Boundary Conflict Register

Current-state refresh: 2026-06-30 (`AXODUS-PORTFOLIO-REQ-01`)

This artifact must be read with the following accepted portfolio delta; older rows and recommendations are historical where they conflict:

- Academy: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D3+` / `COMPLETE_NON_PRODUCTION`.
- Mining: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D3+` / `COMPLETE_NON_PRODUCTION`.
- Defi: `L4_CONSOLIDATED_NON_PRODUCTION` / D-Level `UNASSESSED` / `GATED`; blockers remain open and `ADMIN_MUTATION` remains `UNSAFE`.
- ACS: `L4_READINESS` / `D3+` / `PAUSED`; not L4 Consolidated.
- Marketplace: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D4` / `HOLD / BACKLOG_READY`; Phase 12A is not current priority.
- Next Best Move: `DOCUMENTATION-EPIC-01 - Publication Authority and Versioning Consolidation`.
- No production, execution, treasury, custody, wallet/signing, financial, provider, settlement, payout, billing or contract-write authority is added.

Date: 2026-06-30

Request: CROSS-REQ-04 - Governance & Execution Boundary Review

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This register is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Conflict Model

Conflict values:

- NO_CONFLICT
- DOCUMENTATION_CONFLICT
- OWNERSHIP_CONFLICT
- EXECUTION_CONFLICT
- TREASURY_CONFLICT
- GOVERNANCE_CONFLICT
- PRODUCTION_CONFLICT
- UNKNOWN

## Conflicts Found

The review found boundary conflicts/tensions that are already blocked by existing gates. No conflict grants authority.

| Conflict ID | Conflict Type | Impacted Nuclei | Impacted Opportunities | Severity | Description | Current Control | Recommended Resolution |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| BC-001 | PRODUCTION_CONFLICT | Documentation, all nuclei | OPP-021 | HIGH | Publication readiness exists, but publication authority and root versioning remain unresolved. | Publication remains blocked. | Resolve publication authority/versioning before publication execution. |
| BC-002 | TREASURY_CONFLICT | Defi, Business, Governance, Marketplace, Mining, Lottery, Trading | OPP-005, OPP-013, OPP-015, OPP-018, OPP-022 | CRITICAL | Treasury-sensitive opportunities require approval but formal Treasury/Financial Core ownership is not fully resolved. | Treasury movement remains blocked. | Formalize treasury owner and review path. |
| BC-003 | EXECUTION_CONFLICT | Dex, Business, Defi, AxodusAPP | OPP-006, OPP-019 | HIGH | Dex has read-only L4 readiness while Dex.Country remains execution-sensitive. | Dex execution remains blocked; read-only provider track allowed only. | Keep no-swap boundary and separate any future execution request. |
| BC-004 | EXECUTION_CONFLICT | Trading, ACS, Governance, Defi | OPP-016 | CRITICAL | Trading reached L4 candidate evidence, but live trading, credentials and withdrawals remain blocked. | Execution disabled. | Run credential vault and execution gate review. |
| BC-005 | EXECUTION_CONFLICT | ACS, Core, Governance, Trading | OPP-017 | CRITICAL | ACS has L4 candidate validation, but ACS provisioning/autonomy is not authorized. | ACS execution authority blocked. | Run ACS execution authority and credential boundary review. |
